---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - GitHub Trending">
  <header class="glass" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm mb-4 inline-block hover:underline" style="color: var(--accent);">← Back to Trending</a>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold gradient-text">About</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 page-animate">
    <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">🧠 GitHub Trending</h2>
      <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
        <p>
          This site showcases the hottest GitHub repositories created in the last 30 days,
          ranked by star count. It helps developers discover new and exciting projects gaining
          traction in the open-source community.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6" style="color: var(--text);">How it works</h3>
        <p>
          Data is fetched from the GitHub Search API, querying for repositories created within
          the last 30 days and sorted by star count. The results are rendered as static HTML
          for fast loading and SEO.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6" style="color: var(--text);">Features</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Browse trending repositories by language</li>
          <li>Sort by stars, last updated, or name</li>
          <li>AI-powered repository analysis and comparison</li>
          <li>Responsive design for all devices</li>
          <li>Dark/Light theme with glass morphism effects</li>
          <li>Fast static site generation with Astro</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6" style="color: var(--text);">Tech Stack</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><a href="https://astro.build" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--accent);">Astro</a> - Web framework</li>
          <li><a href="https://tailwindcss.com" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--accent);">Tailwind CSS v4</a> - Styling</li>
          <li><a href="https://api.github.com" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--accent);">GitHub API</a> - Data source</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6" style="color: var(--text);">API Rate Limits</h3>
        <p>
          Without authentication, the GitHub API allows 60 requests per hour. For higher limits
          (5,000/hour), set the <code class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded" style="background: var(--code-bg); color: var(--accent);">GITHUB_TOKEN</code>
          environment variable with a personal access token.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
